Class EarthquakeGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • EarthquakeGroup

  • public class EarthquakeGroup
extends java.lang.Object
    The class EarthquakeGroup represents a group of earthquakes. An instance of type EarthquakeGroup is empty when it is newly constructed, but it can be filled with objects of type Earthquake
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Merlin Unterfinger

      • filterEqMag

        public EarthquakeGroup filterEqMag(java.lang.String op,
                                   double limit)
        This methods filters the earthquakes based on their magnitude. It takes a limit and an arithmetic operator in string format as input.
        Parameters:
        op - an arithmetic operator in string format; either "<", ">" or "lower", "greater"
        limit - (double), the split value
        Returns:
        eqgf An object of type EarthquakeGroup containing the filtered earthquakes.
